# Configurações do WhatsApp API
# Adicione estas variáveis ao seu arquivo .env ou no Render

# =============================================
# OPÇÃO 1: BAILEYS (RECOMENDADO - GRATUITO)
# =============================================
# 1. Execute: cd backend/scripts && bash install-baileys.sh
# 2. Execute: cd baileys-server && npm start
# 3. Escaneie o QR Code com seu WhatsApp
# 4. Configure assim:

WHATSAPP_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/send-message
WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=nao_precisa_para_baileys

# Para produção, use o IP do servidor:
# WHATSAPP_API_URL=http://SEU_IP:3001/send-message

# =============================================
# OPÇÃO 2: Z-API (ALTERNATIVA - GRATUITO)
# =============================================
# 1. Acesse: https://z-api.io
# 2. Crie uma conta e conecte seu WhatsApp
# 3. Copie o Instance ID e Token
# 4. Configure assim:

# WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://api.z-api.io/instances/SEU_INSTANCE_ID/token/SEU_TOKEN/send-text
# WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

# Exemplo real:
# WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://api.z-api.io/instances/3C4F5A6B7C8D9E0F/token/ABC123XYZ789/send-text
# WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=ABC123XYZ789

# =============================================
# OUTRAS OPÇÕES:
# =============================================

# WhatsApp Business API (Facebook):
# WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://graph.facebook.com/v18.0/SEU_PHONE_NUMBER_ID/messages
# WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=seu_access_token_do_facebook

# Twilio WhatsApp:
# WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://api.twilio.com/2010-04-01/Accounts/SEU_ACCOUNT_SID/Messages.json
# WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=seu_auth_token_do_twilio

# Evolution API:
# WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://sua-evolution-api.com/message/sendText
# WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=seu_token_evolution

# =============================================
# COMO OBTER O TOKEN:
# =============================================
# 1. Z-API: https://z-api.io (Gratuito até 100 msg/mês)
# 2. Evolution: https://evolution-api.com (Open Source)
# 3. Baileys: https://github.com/WhiskeySockets/Baileys (Gratuito)
# 4. Twilio: https://twilio.com (Pago)
